		<h1 class="rounded-lg px-3 py-3 text-white text-6xl font-gotham animate-fade-in-text flex sm:justify-center space-x-4 tracking-wider">
		SOCIALS
		</h1>
		<div class="rounded-lg px-3 py-3 text-white text-2xl font-futura animate-fade-in-text flex-col">
		<p class="flex justify-center pt-3 pb-10">You can reach me at the following:</p>
		<div class="flex justify-center text-center">
		<ul class="text-white my-[25px] animate-fade-in-text">
        <a href={"https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-a-81a828153/"}>
            <img src={Linkedin} alt="Linkedin" class="block m-auto"/>
        </a>
        <div class="py-10"></div>
        <a href={"https://github.com/andrew-app"}>
            <img src={Github} alt="Github" class="block m-auto"/>
        </a>
